 Visualize Automation History

 View your automations over time and improve overall automation health using the new automation history dashboard. Get information about automation status, low success rates, and high skip or error counts. Access the report on the new History tab in Automation Studio. This feature is available only in English.

Where: This change applies to all Marketing Cloud Engagement editions.

When: This feature is available on a rolling basis starting in June 2024.
title: Visualizing Marketing Cloud Engagement Automation History
